        "info": "## QPG6200 BLE IoT Demo Integration\n\nAll nodes below this comment are the BLE↔MQTT bridge between the\nQPG6200 development board and the existing Smart Door Devices UI.\n\n### Data Mapping\n| BLE Event | MQTT Topic | Dashboard Effect |\n|---|---|---|\n| PB5 button press | qorvo/demo/button | Doorbell animates + LED flashes |\n| 5s heartbeat | qorvo/demo/heartbeat | Movement Detector turns green |\n| BLE connected | qorvo/demo/status | Speaker/Mic shows active |\n| Light switch ON | qorvo/demo/led | QPG6200 BLUE LED turns on |\n| Doorbell button | qorvo/demo/led | QPG6200 BLUE LED flashes 3s |\n\n### Gateway setup\nRun on the Raspberry Pi:\n  cd ~/ble-demo\n  python3 ble_mqtt_bridge.py",
        "x": 200,
        "y": 1020,
        "wires": []
    },

